0.10.2 (2025-05-27)
===================
* Server - [bug] Fixed inconsistent tooltips for "Configure Additional Options."

0.10.1 (2025-04-21)
===================
* Server - [bug] Fixed PHP errors. (Issue #674)
* Client - [bug] Added missing leases file for ALT OS. (Issue #675)

0.10.0 (2025-01-18)
===================
* Server - [improvement] Made form validation global.
* Server - [improvement] fM 5.0 compatibility.
* Server - [improvement] Provide better configuration logging.
* Server - [improvement] All configuration pages are sortable.
* Server - [improvement] fM 5.0.0-beta3 compatibility.
* Server - [bug] Duplicate lease reservations cannot be made when viewing active leases.
* Server - [bug] Page scrolling fixes.

0.9.0 (2024-09-30)
==================
* Server - [improvement] Updated database tables to the INNODB storage engine. (Issue #607)
* Server - [improvement] Form validations now trims and sanitizes all fields.
* Server - [improvement] Added form validation to input fields.
* Server - [improvement] Added logging for object add/edit.
* Server - [improvement] Added global authoritative option. (Issue #632)
* Server - [improvement] Added quick link icon to view server leases.
* Server - [improvement] Added IP address verification checks.
* Server - [bug] Configuration can no longer be built when the server does not have a
           configuration file defined.
* Server - [bug] Fixed pool creation without being a member.
* Server - [bug] Fixed an issue where 'config_children' was created as a configuration option.
* Server - [bug] Fixed incorrect sanitization of quoted strings.
* Server - [bug] Fixed global option configuration entries.
* Server - [bug] Fixed incorrect automatic population of fields when adding a new object. (Issue #632)
* Server - [bug] Fixed an issue where some JavaScript would not run.
* Client - [improvement] Added client install -o|options parameter. (Issue #605)
* Client - [improvement] Added support to automatically install isc-dhcp-server.
* Client - [improvement] Output formatting changes.
* Both   - [feature] Added ability to quickly delete all leases from a server. (Issue #632)

0.8.1 (2024-05-05)
==================
* Server - [bug] Fixed PHP 8 errors.

0.8.0 (2024-02-09)
==================
* Server - [improvement] CSS/jQuery tweaks to improve the popup boxes.
* Server - [bug] Fixed PHP errors.
* Client - [bug] Removed unused variable reference.

